        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Browse a selection of documentation for new technologies and frameworks introduced at WWDC24. Many existing frameworks have added significant functionality, and you’ll find new ways to enhance your apps targeting the latest platform release.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For a comprehensive list of downloadable sample code projects, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/sample-code",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ". For the latest design guidance localized in multiple languages, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/design/whats-new/",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
